texts.orig: If the account hasn't been created , click "Add New Mail Name" and create the account as usual. Then simply  uncheck the mailbox  option near the bottom. This will create a mail account, but any inbound e-mail for the user is thrown out.
texts.text: If the account hasn't been created , click "Add New Mail Name" and create the account as usual. Then simply  uncheck the mailbox  option near the bottom. This will create a mail account, but any inbound e-mail for the user is thrown out.

texts.label: paragraph
texts.orig: If the e-mail account has already been created , but you want to blackhole any future e-mails, just click the  Mailbox  icon and uncheck the  Mailbox  checkbox on the next page. Click  OK  and any future e-mails are thrown out.
texts.text: If the e-mail account has already been created , but you want to blackhole any future e-mails, just click the  Mailbox  icon and uncheck the  Mailbox  checkbox on the next page. Click  OK  and any future e-mails are thrown out.
